<p>The first is since LDoN patched yesterday i have noticed that Pick Lock skill moved from lvl 40 to lvl 10, so i went ahead and got it (am 30 bard atm)and trained it out in befallen, it wouldn't train anymore when i got it to 125, so dunno if that has changed since the only sites i know with skill cap listing and such is caster's realm and eqdiva, and their listing for that skill cap is atm incorrect.&nbsp;&nbsp;Also Disarm traps which i went and maxed out in Timorous capped at 120 which is inconsistent with those other sites also. Also those other sites say the cap on sense traps is 75 i currently have it at 111, will reach cap soon i assume, and please don't flame me if they've changed these caps awhile ago and am bringing up old stuff, thought they may have switched that too since pick lock went down to lvl 10 skill from lvl 40,  i assume they were made to accomodate the traps and such stuff that came with the LDoN expansion. <br /> <br />Wormius 51 MonkeyLizard <br />Katzaer 30 Rockstar <br />Frawginz 26 Amphibious Meatshield <br />Ubbo 25 Shammy</p>
